page.title: 04APPLETON ROEBUCK WILDLIFE
page.content: { Mammals:}fox,badger,rat,hedgehog,bat field mouse,shrew,mole.rabbit,hare, deer,weasel,{Birds:}sparrow,swallow, house martin, heron,kestrel,gull,owl bullfinch, chaffinch, yellow hammer, robin,lark, starling, greenfinch,jay blue,great,coal & long tailed tits, pied wagtai,gull, blackbird,thrush, fieldfare,lapwing, pheasant,rook,crow partridge,cuckoo,dunnock,pigeon,and winter migrants.{Amphibians:}frog,newt { Invertebrates:}worms,earwigs,centi & millipedes,bees,woodlice,spiders,slugs wasps,various moths,butterflies, flies & aphids,water boatmen,snails,{Flora:} thistle,nettle,cleavers,vetch ,cowslip meadowsweet,dandelion,primrose,reed, various umberliferae & grasses,poppy, buttercup,daisy,speedwell,cuckoo pint assorted fungi, & thousands more. All are waging a continual war with farmer,gardener and suburbanisation.
